<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee2a505b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s348"><num value="348">§ 348.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Agriculture is authorized to make such rules and regulations as may be necessary for carrying out the provisions of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee2a505c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1914-05-08/ch79/s9">May 8, 1914, ch. 79, § 9</ref>, formerly § 8, <ref href="/us/stat/38/374">38 Stat. 374</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1953-06-26/ch157/s1">June 26, 1953, ch. 157, § 1</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/67/85">67 Stat. 85</ref>; renumbered § 9, <ref href="/us/act/1955-08-11/ch798/s1/b">Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 798, § 1(b)</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/69/684">69 Stat. 684</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idee2a505d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idee2a505e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idee2a505f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1953—Act <date date="1953-06-26">June 26, 1953</date>, substituted provisions for rules and regulations for provisions empowering Congress to alter, amend, or repeal sections 341 to 343 and 344 to 348 of this title at any time.</p>
</note>
</notes>
